/grill-with-docs I want to build a trading journal app to help traders to
- Track their growth as a trader through journaling
- Manage their open positions by provide interactive visualizations of both P&L and Risk/Reward that update as the trade plays out
- Gain an intuitive understanding of how option prices change as the market changes
- Manage exits by consider not just original risk/reward but ongoing risk/incremental reward comparisons
- Track the performance of trading a particular underlying, or a strategy across all underlyings, or any other queryable grouping of trades
- Perform daily review of all open positions, including updating closing prices that power the interactive visualizations
- Support complex trade management such as legging into a spread, or scaling in and out of a position
